==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cowish
<hw>Cow"ish</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An umbelliferous
plant (<spn>Peucedanum Cous</spn>) with edible tuberous roots, found in
Oregon.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>cous</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cowitch</ent>⟦br⟧
